Sentencas: The La0.5Sr0.5MnO3 (SLM)-8 mol % yttria stabilized cubic zirconia (YSZ) composite film electrodes were prepared by co-sputtering SLM and YSZ under an argon and oxygen mixed atmosphere.
Titulo: Sputtered La0.5Sr0.5MnO3-yttria stabilized zirconia composite film electrodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity and cathodic overpotential of these composite films were examined.
Titulo: Sputtered La0.5Sr0.5MnO3-yttria stabilized zirconia composite film electrodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The cathodic overpotential of SLM was decreased by co-sputtering SLM and YSZ.
Titulo: Sputtered La0.5Sr0.5MnO3-yttria stabilized zirconia composite film electrodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The addition of YSZ to SLM diminished the grain growth of SLM by annealing at a high temperature.
Titulo: Sputtered La0.5Sr0.5MnO3-yttria stabilized zirconia composite film electrodes for SOFC
